    "Simultaneously, we acknowledge the inherent challenge of achieving absolute comprehensiveness and recognizing potential omissions or biases.",
    "Excluding other datasets, for example, Google Scholar, may cause the omission of a few articles.",
    "However, on the other hand, Scopus provides unbiased, reliable, and standard articles from reputed journals.",
